snippet: Top-ranked golfer Luke Donald finished Friday’s second round of the United States Open at 11 over par, a score that eliminated him from this weekend’s final rounds.
abstract: Luke Donald and Rory McIlroy fail to make the cut at the United States Open golf tournament.
lead_paragraph: Top-ranked golfer Luke Donald finished Friday’s second round of the United States Open at 11 over par, a score that eliminated him from this weekend’s final rounds.
